title: DDFP 485: 'Dead or Alive' & College Football Predictions with A.J. Hawk
itunes:title: DDFP 485: 'Dead or Alive' & College Football Predictions with A.J. Hawk
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank, Matt Harmon and former Packers and Bengals linebacker A.J. Hawk to discuss the Vikings' backup quarterback situation, the best college football matchups this weekend and their predictions for the college playoff. Then, NFL Fantasy Analyst Michael Fabiano joins the show to play a game of "Dead or Alive" featuring Tony Romo's career as a starter, overall interest in Tim Tebow and the controversial zero running back fantasy draft strategy. Plus, Shek wraps the show with a new NFC wild card themed edition of "Elimination Chamber."
